task.summary: Lots of fixes and cleanup, laying groundwork for scales.
Scales coming along, max amplitude = sound quality ++
Major sound fix, was doubling signals (+= to self). Main problem now: in musical mode there is constant clipping because the same signal is being added to itself many times if pixel width > 1.
Moving WebWorker (sound.signals.worker.js) and dependencies to public so they don't get concatenated - WebWorker needs to import on a script-by-script basis for now.
